sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin as Administrator
    participant Login as Login Interface
    participant Auth as Authentication Service
    participant DB as Database
    participant Dash as Admin Dashboard

    Admin->>Login: Enter credentials
    Login->>Auth: Submit login request
    Auth->>DB: Verify credentials & role
    DB-->>Auth: Role = admin
    Auth-->>Dash: Grant admin session
    Dash-->>Admin: Render admin dashboard

    Admin->>Dash: Manage Users
    Dash->>DB: Update user_roles
    Admin->>Dash: Manage Content (CMS)
    Dash->>DB: Update blog_posts / site content
    Admin->>Dash: Generate Reports
    Dash->>DB: Query audit_log & analytics
    Admin->>Dash: Logout
    Dash->>Auth: Invalidate session
